GraphQL-From-Struct
===================

A simple one-method library makes a `GraphQL <https://graphql.org/>`__
query from Python data structures.

Table of Contents
-----------------

1. `Installation`_
2. `Usage`_
3. `Exceptions`_
4. `Parameters`_
5. `Reserved keywords`_
6. `Examples`_

-  `Fields`_
-  `Arguments`_
-  `Default arguments`_
-  `Aliases`_
-  `Fragments`_
-  `Using variables inside fragments`_
-  `Operation name`_
-  `Variables`_
-  `Default variables`_
-  `Directives`_
-  `Mutations`_
